DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T2.value name, T1.ZeroInflationIndexCurve, T1.id FROM ORE.dbo.TodaysMarketZeroInflationIndexCurves T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T2 ON T1.name = T2.value

field.name: *name
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value name, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value
